components.templateData:
<lai-step-group-header>
  <lai-step-label
    *ngFor="let step of steps; let index = index"
    [step]="step"
    [selected]="step === selectedStep"
    [ngClass]="{'previous': index < activeIndex, 'next': index > activeIndex} "
    (selectedChange)="onSelectedChange(index)">
  </lai-step-label>
</lai-step-group-header>

<lai-step-group-body
  *ngIf="selectedStep"
  [step]="selectedStep"></lai-step-group-body>

      <lai-tab-group [size]="size"

        <lai-tab *ngFor="let item of data; let last = last"
                 [label]="item.label"
                 [disabled]="last">
          {{ item.content }}
        </lai-tab>
      </lai-tab-group>
    `,
  }),
}
